                                "stop": 16.702,
                                "byte_start": 76800,
                                "byte_stop": 143673,
                                "text": "The disposition of two cases 72-1597, Beasley against Food Fair of North Carolina and 73-157, Calero-Toledo against Pearson Yacht Leasing Co will be announced by Mr. Justice Brennan."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 16.702,
                        "stop": 71.607,
